value.0: Mykes Lamplighter is the Castellan of the Keep. He runs the general staff and also tallies the guild votes.
Serah Blackhand is the guildmaster of the landowner's guild.
The Stan is a half orc former adventurer who runs "The Trades" an employment business that pays adventurers to do what they do best. He is also the guildmaster for trades.
